c: 11
v: 61
t: "Bo ab'ekika kya Thamud twabatumira Muganda waabwe Swaleh, naagamba nti abange bantu bange musinze Katonda temulinaayo kintu kyonna kigwanidde kusinzibwa okugyako yye, yye yeeyabatandikawo ng’abaggya mu nsi, ate naabakwasa obuyinza okugikulaakulanya, kale mumwegayirire, era mwenenye, mudde gyali mazima Mukama omulabirizi wange ali kumpi ayanukula (abamusaba)"